---
title: Beef Mince Tortilla Stack with Charred Corn & Cucumber Salsa
description: You're going to want to pile your plate up high with this tasty tortilla stack, which happens to be filled with delicious beef, cooked in a richly spiced tomato sauce. Don't forget to serve with a dollop of plant-based mayo!
